exports[`Auto Convert Inline to Macro (autoConvertInlineToMacro) > Compilation Tests (AST Snapshots) > should output block scopes even if autoConvert is true, because the argument is impure > fixtures/auto-macro-fallback.ts-fallback 1`] = `
"let i = 5;
